This library includes MiGBase64, a BSD licensed base64 encoder & decoder
by Mikael Grev. See src/tiled/util/Base64.java for licensing details.

http://www.mapeditor.org/

----------
 Building
----------

To make libtiled.jar, install Maven (http://maven.apache.org/), and run the
following command:
$ mvn clean install

To run all unit-tests, run the following command:
$ mvn test

To generate reports and documentation, run:
$ mvn site
